<subSubSection pageId="19" pageNumber="350" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="19.[151,1436,151,393]" pageId="19" pageNumber="350">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,331,357]" pageId="19" pageNumber="350">Etymology.</emphasis>
The specific epithet of the new species is derived from the Latin 
<emphasis box="[1070,1182,331,357]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="350">papillatus</emphasis>
, referring to the shape of the dorsoapical lobe of the sacculus.
</paragraph>
